title: BIG FACTS feat. LIL SCRAPPY

description:
Is reality TV the graveyard for the career of a music artist? The BIG FACTS crew discusses and debates this on this episode. Love and Hip-Hop cast member and rapper LIL SCRAPPY joins this converstation. SCRAPPY also speaks on the streets, new music, future endeavors and more!
